  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Heavy rains in Sabaragamuwa and Central Provinces",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology says that there will be occasional rain or thundershowers in Sabaragamuwa and Central Provinces today (22).",
        "A spokesman of the department said that there will be several periods of rain in the Western and North-Western provinces.",
        "The spokesman said that scattered rain or thundershowers will occur in other areas in the evening or during the night.",
        "The spokesperson said that in some places in Sabaragamuwa, Central, Eastern, North Central and Uva provinces, more than 75 mm of heavy rain will occur.",
        "The department also states that thunderstorms may be accompanied by lightning and temporary gusty winds."
      ],
